= Webdoc

== Instruction for development installation

Dependencies:

- Ruby 1.8.6
- RubyGems 1.3.6
- Rails 2.3.5
- Rake
- SQlite3 (on Windows, install sqlite3 and ruby gem for mswin32 from http://rubyforge.org/frs/?group_id=254)

Run in working repository:

  sudo gem install bundler
  sudo bundle install

Create a sym link to app/javascripts

 On MacOSX or Linux fom the public/app folder do
   ln -s ../../app/javascripts/ javascripts
 On Windows vista or 7 from the public/app folder do
   mklink /D javascripts ..\app\javascripts
 On Windows XP sym link does not exist and you must modify config/assets.yml with
   package_assets: always
 
   
If all tests pass, you can work on a big new feature ;-)


== Plugins

= How to ask for a merge request
Push your commit to the repository.
git push 
Then login to Assembla. In the Source/Git tab click on the Forks tab then click button send a merge request.

